    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The horror at the end of the abyss has brainwashed every sea creature with its psychic powers. Everyone but you. Guided by your only friend, a penny-pinching seagull, you must sail the oceans to face its minions and break their curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319040/extras/a8a9f2258f43e1064ba7fff02c97e0d9.poster.avif?t=1735110647\" width=718 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319040/extras/a8a9f2258f43e1064ba7fff02c97e0d9.webm?t=1735110647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319040/extras/a8a9f2258f43e1064ba7fff02c97e0d9.mp4?t=1735110647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brief runs (around 3 minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable characters with their own set of weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses at every level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 different companions with unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetic skins for your fish</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mighty single-use power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard and golden extra hard difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless hordes mode and boss rush mode available</p></li></ul>",
